videos.description: Devon Dotson picks off a pass and finishes the fastbreak with a one-handed jam to give Kansas an early lead.
videos.headline: Dotson comes away with steal and flush with one hand

videos.description: Oklahoma State's Isaac Likekele spins through defenders to finish at the rim with a lay in.
videos.headline: Likekele spins through lane for layup

videos.description: Cameron McGriff ties the game with huge 3-pointer but Devon Dotson sprints down the court and finishes a tough layup in traffic to give Kansas the lead.
videos.headline: Dotson speeds for tough layup after KU loses lead

videos.description: Mitch Lightfoot flushes a putback for Kansas as the Jayhawks steal momentum.
videos.headline: Lightfoot throws down putback jam

videos.description: Oklahoma State's Cameron McGriff comes away with a steal to throw down a hard jam.
videos.headline: McGriff hammers one-handed slam
